Type: Package
Title: Table Rendering with flextable, kable and gt
Version: 0.1.0
Description: This package provides a unified interface for rendering tables using 'flextable', 'gt', and 'kable' libraries, with customizable options for font sizes, bold text, alignment, and different output formats such as HTML, PDF, and DOCX.
